question.input: Capture an AFM image with dimensions $\pu{500 nm} \times \pu{500 nm}$ at a scan angle of $ 5 degrees $, using the following parameters: P gain = 100, I gain = 5000, D gain = 0, and setpoint = 0.1 V. Then, open the latest file in the current folder; from that file, extract the Z-axis backward image data and calculate the area of the image.
